Lifecycle owner component : UI components like activities / fragments
Lifecycle : the life cycle data structure, which can be observed, provided by lifecycle owener
Lifecycle observer observes lifecycle owner component's life cycle , annoted methods

LiveData = observables (data stream, transformation) + has relationshio to lifecycle aware (so that can control when to notify Observer / stop )
    -> the observe function requires observer and a lifecycle owner

ViewModel = data provider that persists across UI components configuration changes 
            provide livedata to UI components

Room - > API for ORM in android , provide CRUD annotation , return livedata 

